verbose_text: At 1 and 2 weeks, the expression levels of the BGLAP gene in the SaOS-2 cells cultured on n-HAP / Col specimens were higher than those of cells cultured on m-HAP / Col and Col specimens (p < 0.05), indicating that the n-HAP particles in the n-HAP / Col composites had the ability to rapidly induce late-stage osteogenic differentiation.
